        <mxCell id="IXJTp3MiV_YSEwoRgoHY-15" parent="r1gQPhgy6ZG2-IyFKPIZ-37" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;absoluteArcSize=1;arcSize=14;strokeWidth=2;align=left;" value="&lt;span style=&quot;float: none; display: inline !important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(236, 236, 236);&quot;&gt;AI readiness is displaying the first time the user enter the website guidance information ie :&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div&gt;&quot;Hi i am an AI Agent dedicated to support you and your team with hints and recomendations to solve your case in an optimal and structured manner faster by reasoning on existing cases in the database and will provide you hints based on my training data ( they will be marked explicitly).... To ensure you can use this agent correctly providing meaninfull answers please focus your questions on the following categories :&lt;br&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(236, 236, 236);&quot;&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Questions asking for guidance on an existing case (currently open in the UI) ?&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Questions asking for a new problem if there where relevant cases in the past and how they could be solved giving you tips how to structure your case&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Questions related to overall strategy on how to prevent similar cases in the future focusing on organizational , process &amp;amp; technology&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Questions related to case performance in your country or global&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;pre-requisites : strategy reasoning is only possible if your organisation loads organizational, process , operational and technical data&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="240" width="600" x="130" y="13" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="r1gQPhgy6ZG2-IyFKPIZ-44" parent="1" style="swimlane;startSize=20;horizontal=0;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;" value="PREVENTION &amp;amp; STRATEGY" vertex="1">
