        <mxCell id="IXJTp3MiV_YSEwoRgoHY-5" parent="r1gQPhgy6ZG2-IyFKPIZ-44" style="whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" value="Before answering to the user/team the LLM React using a secondary prompt to the LLM ensuring the answer is consistent and structured&amp;nbsp;&lt;div&gt;&lt;ol&gt;&lt;li&gt;There is a pydantic class for the reply structure&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;the LLM answer is providing specific context from the question&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;the LLM answer is providing overall strategy guidelines&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;the LLM can only search for information using the hybrid_retriever from the case evidence and knowledge indexes IF NECESSARY ie the agent node must REACT&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
