        <mxCell id="IXJTp3MiV_YSEwoRgoHY-10" parent="1" style="whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;verticalAlign=top;align=left;" value="Reason on question by searching on past cases (case_search_index_v3)&lt;div&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;If the user/ team enters a question on KPI&#39; performance the LLM should ask if the user wants to have KPI&#39;s calculated for a specific country or global and compere them&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Key KPI&#39;s to be calculated are related to&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Average Duration of cases in total and or per state D1 - D8 in a particular country or global&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;% of similar cases in the past in country or global&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
